                        h2 Why is knowledge management important?
                        p.lead
                            | Though employees, customers, and overall businesses benefit from an organised knowledge management system, it particularly improves the overall customer experience. Plus, establishing a comprehensive knowledge management system is pivotal in empowering customers to help themselves and enhancing the overall customer experience

        section.bg-light
            .container.px-4
